      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "【动作】 完整覆盖脚手架默认的 src/app/layout.tsx：\n\n**直接把下面内容完整覆盖** `agenthub/src/app/layout.tsx`：\n\n```tsx\nimport type { Metadata } from \"next\";\nimport { Inter, JetBrains_Mono } from \"next/font/google\";\nimport { Header, Footer } from \"@/components/layout\";\nimport \"./globals.css\";\n\nconst inter = Inter({\n  subsets: [\"latin\"],\n  variable: \"--font-inter\",\n  weight: [\"400\", \"500\", \"600\", \"700\"],\n  display: \"swap\",\n});\n\nconst jetbrainsMono = JetBrains_Mono({\n  subsets: [\"latin\"],\n  variable: \"--font-jetbrains-mono\",\n  weight: [\"400\", \"500\"],\n  display: \"swap\",\n});\n\nexport const metadata: Metadata = {\n  title: \"AgentHub · AI Agent 商店与 Playground\",\n  description: \"下一代 AI Agent 构建、编排与分发平台\",\n};\n\nexport default function RootLayout({ children }: { children: React.ReactNode }) {\n  return (\n    <html lang=\"zh-CN\" className={`${inter.variable} ${jetbrainsMono.variable}`}>\n      <body className=\"flex min-h-screen flex-col bg-bg-base font-sans text-fg-default antialiased\">\n        <Header />\n        <main className=\"flex-1\">{children}</main>\n        <Footer />\n      </body>\n    </html>\n  );\n}\n```\n\n> **为啥不加 Noto_Sans_SC**：Next 16 + Turbopack 对 Noto_Sans_SC CJK 子集有 bug，中文走系统字体 fallback（`PingFang SC` / `Microsoft YaHei`，在 globals.css 里配）\n\n---",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "【动作】 完整覆盖脚手架默认的 src/app/layout.tsx：\n\n**直接把下面内容完整覆盖** `agenthub/src/app/layout.tsx`：\n\n```tsx\nimport type { Metadata } from \"next\";\nimport { Inter, JetBrains_Mono } from \"next/font/google\";\nimport { Header, Footer } from \"@/components/layout\";\nimport \"./globals.css\";\n\nconst inter = Inter({\n  subsets: [\"latin\"],\n  variable: \"--font-inter\",\n  weight: [\"400\", \"500\", \"600\", \"700\"],\n  display: \"swap\",\n});\n\nconst jetbrainsMono = JetBrains_Mono({\n  subsets: [\"latin\"],\n  variable: \"--font-jetbrains-mono\",\n  weight: [\"400\", \"500\"],\n  display: \"swap\",\n});\n\nexport const metadata: Metadata = {\n  title: \"AgentHub · AI Agent 商店与 Playground\",\n  description: \"下一代 AI Agent 构建、编排与分发平台\",\n};\n\nexport default function RootLayout({ children }: { children: React.ReactNode }) {\n  return (\n    <html lang=\"zh-CN\" className={`${inter.variable} ${jetbrainsMono.variable}`}>\n      <body className=\"flex min-h-screen flex-col bg-bg-base font-sans text-fg-default antialiased\">\n        <Header />\n        <main className=\"flex-1\">{children}</main>\n        <Footer />\n      </body>\n    </html>\n  );\n}\n```\n\n> **为啥不加 Noto_Sans_SC**：Next 16 + Turbopack 对 Noto_Sans_SC CJK 子集有 bug，中文走系统字体 fallback（`PingFang SC` / `Microsoft YaHei`，在 globals.css 里配）\n\n---",
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
      "autoResize": true
    },
