      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "【动作】 两步操作（UI + 复制 fileKey）：\n\n**操作**：\n\n1. 打开 <https://www.figma.com/settings>\n2. 左栏选 **Security**\n3. 滚到 **Personal access tokens**\n4. 点 **Generate new token**：\n   - Token name：`agenthub-mcp`（或随便）\n   - Expiration：`7 days`（学习期够）/ 生产选更长\n   - **Scopes 至少勾**：\n     - ✅ `file_content:read`（\"Read the contents of and render images from files\"）\n     - ✅ `library_assets:read`（\"Read data about individual components and styles\"，在 **Design systems** 分组）\n5. 点 **Generate token** → **立刻复制**那串 `figd_xxxxxxxxx...`（只显示一次）\n\n---\n\n─── 接下来 ───\n\n**操作**：\n\n1. <https://www.figma.com/files/> → 右上角 **`+`** → **Design file**（**不是** Figma Make / FigJam）\n2. 文件会默认叫 `Untitled`，保持即可\n3. **复制浏览器地址栏 URL**，形如 `https://www.figma.com/design/XXXXXXXXX/Untitled?...`——`/design/` 后面那串就是 **`FIGMA_FILE_KEY`**\n\n---",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "【动作】 两步操作（UI + 复制 fileKey）：\n\n**操作**：\n\n1. 打开 <https://www.figma.com/settings>\n2. 左栏选 **Security**\n3. 滚到 **Personal access tokens**\n4. 点 **Generate new token**：\n   - Token name：`agenthub-mcp`（或随便）\n   - Expiration：`7 days`（学习期够）/ 生产选更长\n   - **Scopes 至少勾**：\n     - ✅ `file_content:read`（\"Read the contents of and render images from files\"）\n     - ✅ `library_assets:read`（\"Read data about individual components and styles\"，在 **Design systems** 分组）\n5. 点 **Generate token** → **立刻复制**那串 `figd_xxxxxxxxx...`（只显示一次）\n\n---\n\n─── 接下来 ───\n\n**操作**：\n\n1. <https://www.figma.com/files/> → 右上角 **`+`** → **Design file**（**不是** Figma Make / FigJam）\n2. 文件会默认叫 `Untitled`，保持即可\n3. **复制浏览器地址栏 URL**，形如 `https://www.figma.com/design/XXXXXXXXX/Untitled?...`——`/design/` 后面那串就是 **`FIGMA_FILE_KEY`**\n\n---",
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
      "autoResize": true
    },
